Astrotrain nods and says to Motormaster, "Just as it should be."
Then he turns to the new bots and goes over to meet them.
"And who are you bots? We are interested in some sort of alliance. 
Being new here we would like to exchange information."



> "Then you can handle public relations" Motormaster spits.
